	<div class="commentBody">
		<div id="comment_body_65025207">And that 250 billion is just the estimate. Nuclear construction and cleanup costs have a way of uncontrollably ballooning up to near infinity. I really want nuclear to work. I consider myself pro nuclear.  But that 0.08 number is a pipe dream that ignores near-infinite risk at both ends of project life.</div>
